strings: <voice_0x01001565><se_def>*: You! This will be the last time you rebel against the Grand Master!
<voice_0x01001561><center>Now it's time to use my power!
The soul of the fledgling Godbird speaks to <hero>!

<voice_0x01001568><se_def>Marcello: Persistence is not a virtue!
Something you obviously never learnt.
<voice_0x0100156A><se_def>Marcello: This will be the last time! You will know my true might and grovel at my feet!
